# Copy to `.env.local` and adjust values (`.env.local` is gitignored).
# Astro loads: `.env`, `.env.local`, `.env.[mode]`, `.env.[mode].local`
# https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/environment-variables/

# --- Letterboxd (optional; server/build only — no PUBLIC_ prefix) ---
# Profile: plain links in footer, About, and media review pages.
# RSS: build-time fetch; “recent activity” list only on `template: media-review` posts.
# URL shape: https://letterboxd.com/<username>/ and https://letterboxd.com/<username>/rss/
# LETTERBOXD_PROFILE_URL=https://letterboxd.com/yourusername/
# LETTERBOXD_RSS_URL=https://letterboxd.com/yourusername/rss/

# --- Remark42 (optional; defaults match production if unset) ---
# PUBLIC_REMARK42_HOST=https://notes.antoniwan.online/api/remark42
# PUBLIC_REMARK42_SITE_ID=remark42
